I've never snowboarded either, but my husband is a snowboarder. Well, I was wondering if you could

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:54.880
give us a good example of sort of the type of problem that your team works on. You don't have

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:59.519
to be super specific if you don't want to or you can't be, but I think it would be helpful to

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:03.760
understand the types of problems that you work on and also the type of data that you have access to

00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:09.119
use. That way we can sort of form some context around this, because we come from all different

